lenders.name: Claudine
lenders.occupational_info:
I'm Claudine and I am a Brighton based wedding photographer. In addition to weddings, I also shoot fashion, family portraits, maternity shots, and children and babies. I not only shoot weddings, but I also offer packages for family portraiture, pregnancy, kids, and fashion. Your wedding day is essential to you, which is why having your wedding day photographed by the right individual is vital. 

After all the planning and effort you have placed into your wedding, you need the right photographer there to record every detail of your special day. Which explains why I have put on display my very best on my website, hopefully making the selection easy for you. My job is much like offering up a treasure chest of amazing images that will help to keep your memories forever. I'm in love with love, and you can say I'm addicted! Even after being in the photography business for more than ten years I still never grow tired of seeing a couple pledge their love, kiss their new baby, or celebrate life together as a family. 

I started studying film photography more than ten years back in Nyc, and I immediately loved the magic of dark r oom processing. I have since also fallen in love with digital photography, although I maintain my lifelong love for film. I am at my most relaxed when behind the camera and many of my clients feel the calming effects of my unobtrusive and professional presence. Even though I spend a lot of the year photographing UK based weddings, I spend several months in the US and Europe for weddings and other commercial jobs, so catch me if you can! Client spaces fill up fast, so please go to my website http://www.momentscaptured.co.uk and contact me today regarding your very own wedding! 

Contact address: 
Moments Captured Photography 
6 Cleveland Rd Brighton, East Sussex BN1 6FF 
07799 796707 momentscaptured.co.uk
